<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Lalpa Isun Ti a</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mi kuole tuia leh Thagau a,
 Piengthak lo chu (2)
 Pathien gam mi hitak ahi puo,
 Lalpa Isu'n a ti a.

[V2]
 Kuole Amah ging chun,
 Kumsawt hinna nei ding;
 Kuole a mah ging chun,
 Kumsawt hinna kumsawt hin nei un au.

[V3]
 2. Kuole lei lehna a khut nga a,
 Nunglam en chu (2)
 Pathien gam mi hitak ahi puoi,
 Lalpa Isu'n a ti a.

[V4]
 3. Kuole nicheng amah kraws pu a,
 Ei zui lo chu (2)
 Pathien gam mi hitak ahi puoi,
 Lalpa Isu'n a ti a.

[V5]
 4. Nicheng Lalpa hun zui zel ing ka;
 Gimum mahleh (2)
 Thagau Thiengtho in ei pui zelin;
 Na gam ka tun masieh in.

[V6]
 Kuole amah zui chun,
 Kumsawt chawlhna chang ding;
 Lopina vak achun kumsawt nawpna,
 Tawp lo chu chang unau.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>313</hymn_number>
</song>